Images to base64

Source: R/dev-utils.R
image_to_base64.Rd

encodes images into base64 strings.

Usage

image_to_base64(filepaths)

Arguments

filepaths

file names.

Examples

rlogo <- file.path( R.home("doc"), "html", "logo.jpg")
image_to_base64(rlogo)
